longer traded separately, though they remain in use. Based on euro 
rates, the dollar is worth 1.8448 German marks, down from 1.8542; 
6.1871 French francs, down from 6.2188; 2.0786 Dutch guilders, down 
from 2.0892; 1,826.33 Italian lire, down from 1,835.68. 
