<P>
	YONKERS, N.Y. (AP) -- Self Possessed, who set a world record in  
winning the Hambletonian, is bypassing the Yonkers Trot, the second 
leg of the Triple Crown. 
</P>
<P>
	The 3-year-old colt ran a 1:51 3/5 at the Hambletonian, but will  
