<HEADLINE> AP Corrects Frank Oz Story </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- In an Aug. 11 story about  
puppeteer-turned-filmmaker Frank Oz, The Associated Press 
incorrectly stated that Oz was the puppeteer for the character 
Kermit the Frog in the film ``Muppets From Space.'' In fact, Steve 
