<HEADLINE> Driver in Ky. Crash To Be Freed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	FRANKFORT, Ky. (AP) -- The man who caused the nation's deadliest  
drunken-driving crash is getting out of prison. 
</P>
