<HEADLINE> Angels Recall Pitcher Ramon Ortiz </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CHICAGO (AP) -- Right-hander Ramon Ortiz was recalled from  
Triple-A Edmonton on Saturday by the Anaheim Angels, who optioned 
right-hander Mike Fyhrie to Edmonton. 
</P>
<P>
	Ortiz, 23, made his major league debut Thursday when he started  
for the Angels against the Chicago White Sox. Ortiz was 5-3 with a 
4.05 ERA in nine starts for Edmonton. 
</P>
<P>
	Fyhrie was 0-3 with a 4.88 ERA in 10 games, including four  
starts, for the Angels. 
  	   	
</P>
